SetInCountry: India
Category: A decision that pushed me to the edge
AuthorName: Sushil Sonawane
AuthorCountry: India
Text: We are studied one day in night.So discussed about one concept that time slightly
  turns towards picnic subject and we all leave study.We are going to discuss various
  spots for picnic but no one get interesting in selected picnic spots. That time
  I gave an idea about adventure trip by bicycle so all are showing interest on my
  idea. After completion of our exam we plan the adventure successfully and upto 80
  km with lots of enjoy. I was such a memorable adventure.
